metadata.name: Lucky 888 Cats #1
metadata.description:
The Lucky 888 Cats is an exclusive total collection of 8,888 lucky cats. 88 NFT's are hand-drawn Master Cats (Genesis Collection), & 8,800 are random generated composed of multiple traits resulting in common, uncommon, rare's and ultra-rare NFT's; bringing you good fortune, health & happiness!

Staking of each Lucky 888 Cat NFT will gain access to private IRL networking events, merch drops, giveaways, future whitelists, & income-revenue sharing opportunities in the Lucky Cats casino and the metaverse real estate.
